Hey there, and welcome to DCTC! We are Disney Cars Toy Club and we love, love, love making super fun, kid-friendly videos! 

Some of our favorite things include Olaf, Queen Elsa and Princess Anna (and anything Frozen, actually), Mater (you know…Tow Mater - from Disney Pixar’s Cars and Cars 2), Play Doh, Surprise Eggs, Kinder Eggs, Chocolate (and chocolate eggs!), Roc (our crazy dog - you'll see him in videos sometimes), Lightning McQueen, Blind Bags, Hello Kitty (meow!), Sofia the First, Monster High (love Goulia's glasses!), BARBIE (as long as she’s not too crazy), Playdough (wait...did we say that already?). We also love color-changing toys, My Little Pony (MLP), Littlest Petshop, and all things Disney! And guess what? We can’t wait to hear more about you and what YOU like!

So, you know what that means, right? You have to leave us comments! Or... drop us a line here:

DCTC
PO Box 104
Saxapahaw, NC 27340

Business Inquiries Email: Seecommercial@gmail.com

snippet.title: EnriqueIglesiasVEVO
snippet.description: Enrique Iglesias turns up the heat again on his tenth full-length album SEX AND LOVE. Boasting sizzling singles such as "I'm A Freak" featuring Pitbull, it's the Grammy Award-winning international superstar's sexiest work to date. He never fails to satisfy though. His overall sales surpass 100 million albums worldwide, making him one of the best-selling Spanish artists ever. His legacy includes five Top 5 singles on theBillboard Hot 100 with two landing at #1. He also boasts 13 number ones on theBillboard Dance Chart, which is the most for any male performer in the chart's history. In total, he's enjoyed seventy number ones across all Billboard charts. Plus, he holds the record for "Most #1 Spanish Language Singles" on the Hot Latin Tracks Chart with 23. Enrique doesn't plan on slowing down or stopping any time soon either. SEX AND LOVE is something that his audience wants—and even needs—and he's giving it right to them.

snippet.title: Ultra Music
snippet.description: Ultra Music, since 1996 has proven itself to be the label which has consistently developed electronic artists to major worldwide success. We have made it past the 16 year mark, and we are moving strongly and proudly into the future. Ultra Music is a Grammy Award winning music company and the winner of Best American Dance Label from 2005 through 2011. Ultra Music also has the number one YouTube channel for electronic music that boasts over 3 billion views. We at Ultra have a passion for electronic music and believe we continue to succeed at sharing that passion with our fans. Ultra is certain to keep one step ahead in the world of dance music and remain the leading independent electronic label in the world with offices in New York, Toronto, Los Angeles and London.

snippet.title: Super Simple Songs
snippet.description:
Nursery rhymes and original kids songs that are easy-to-teach, easy-to-learn, and super fun! Our videos are intended for teachers and parents of young learners with developing speaking skills, ideal for sharing with Pre-K children and younger, young ESL/EFL learners, and children with special needs. 

The songs are appropriately paced for children with developing motor skills, and full of room for gestures and dancing to help kids interact with the lyrics.

We hope you'll enjoy these songs with the young learners in your life. Let us know how it goes!

snippet.title: TheEngineeringFamily
snippet.description:
TheEngineeringFamily is designed by a husband and wife duo...Mr. Engineer is an experienced engineer who loves exploring new things. Mrs. Engineer is an award winning teacher with a focus on math and counselling. Finally, we have our Assistant who loves to make videos and create fun stories that make children laugh.

We focus on three things 

Educational Fun - As parents we try to infuse elements of learning into everything that we do.

The Coolest Toys - Not necessarily the most popular but the toys that we like the best

Fun Stories and surprises - We create original stories using some of your favorite characters to help inspire imaginative play.

 You can rest assured that we take the "Family" in "TheEngineeringFamily" very seriously. Our channel focuses on fun, safe, and educational play while avoiding anything that hints of innuendo or borderline content. 


Your Friends,
TheEngineeringFamily

snippet.title: Sesame Street
snippet.description:
Welcome to Sesame Street. If, by some chance, you were looking for Elmo, Cookie Monster, Big Bird, Grover, Oscar, Bert & Ernie, Telly, Zoe, Rosita, Baby Bear and Snuffleupagus, you are in luck because they are all here! Subscribe for new videos every week:

Music on Mondays!

Celebrities on Tuesdays!

Muppet Fun on Wednesdays!

Classic Sesame on Thursdays!

Furchester on Fridays!

For more fun games and videos for your preschooler in a safe, child-friendly environment, visit us at http://www.sesamestreet.org

Sesame Street is a production of Sesame Workshop, a nonprofit educational organization. Sesame Street reaches millions of children every day in more than 150 countries. The Workshop's mission is to use the educational power of media to help children everywhere reach their highest potential. The Workshop's programs are tailored to the needs of specific regions and focus on topics that help young children and families develop critical skills for lifelong learning.
